    "Name": "Hunchback",
    "Details": "One of three custom Hunchbacks built by the Laramie brothers of the Oberon Confederation, this variant replaces the signature autocannon with twin ATM 12 launchers carrying both extended range and high explosive munitions. The flexibility to switch between range brackets mid-engagement made it the most tactically versatile of the three builds. A Medium Laser and Small Laser handle close-range backup when the missiles run dry.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Battle Fists</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.04</color></b>",
